metadata.name: WRAPPED FUTURE #4
metadata.description:
1/1 NFT - embracing change.  3840x2160 PNG.

This NFT series called “Wrapped Future” represent pivotal moments of change: sometimes we take decisions through personal and past experiences that wrap around us acting as a filter in our decision-making process.

Marble and Glass are here representing the past, controlling not only our decisions, but also our feelings, thus keeping us stuck in the same place mentally and physically.

Gold represents the future, in #4 morphing the past into the future, reaching for light.
